---
/**
 * SolveSection.astro
 *
 * "We Solve" section with centered problem statements on dark background.
 * Migrated from Next.js SolveSection to Astro with proper BEM styling.
 *
 * Content source: docs/softforge-links/content-architecture.md
 * Design source: docs/softforge-links/design-direction.md (Pebble Flow centered layouts)
 *
 * Layout:
 * - 100vh full viewport height, vertically centered (section--viewport)
 * - Pine green background with gradient overlay (::before)
 * - Centered content (max-width: 900px via --content-narrow)
 * - Simple checkmarks (CSS ::before with gradient)
 * - Scannable problem statements with AISEO-optimized parenthetical details
 *
 * Typography:
 * - Section heading: Comfortaa 700, gradient-text-light (heading-1 class)
 * - Problem statements: body-text-lg, parchment color at 90% opacity
 *
 * Accessibility:
 * - Semantic section with aria-labelledby
 * - Proper heading hierarchy (h2 within main)
 * - High contrast: parchment on pine (10.2:1, exceeds WCAG AA 4.5:1)
 * - List uses role="list" for screen reader clarity
 *
 * Styles: src/styles/components/solve.css
 */

import '../../styles/components/solve.css';
---

<section id="solve" class="solve section--viewport" aria-labelledby="solve-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 id="solve-heading" class="solve__label heading-1 gradient-text-light">We Solve</h2>

    <ul class="solve__list" role="list">
      <li class="solve__item body-text-lg">Slow sites killing conversions</li>
      <li class="solve__item body-text-lg">WCAG 2.1 AA deadlines without panic (accessibility audits, screen reader testing, semantic HTML)</li>
      <li class="solve__item body-text-lg">Turning maps, GPS, and real-world data into storytelling (Mapbox routing, geocoding, offline maps, real-time tracking)</li>
      <li class="solve__item body-text-lg">AI development workflows that actually help (AI-assisted development, discovery optimization, context setup)</li>
      <li class="solve__item body-text-lg">Taking your build exactly where you envisioned (custom code for no-code/low-code platforms, API integrations, advanced features)</li>
      <li class="solve__item body-text-lg">Wiring together complex integrations (third-party APIs, real-time data feeds, multi-platform architectures)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
